ğŸ§  In Simple Terms

Azure IAM = Who (Identity) + What (Role) + Where (Scope)

Example:

Vidya (User) â†’ Contributor (Role) â†’ Resource Group â€œWebApp-RGâ€ (Scope)

This means Vidya can manage resources inside â€œWebApp-RGâ€ but cannot modify IAM settings.

